verbose_text: XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR A heterodimeric partner of small Maf, the transcription factor nuclear factor E2 p45 related factor-2 (Nrf2), displays decreased expression during chondrocyte differentiation and inhibits numerous aspects of chondrocyte differentiation in vitro.
